{"tid":1785430,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"［口交部寫稿？］網傳警方沙角邨後樓梯遺下手槍　警：只是汽槍　別有用心假消息煽動憎恨警方","createTime":"2019-12-16T11:05:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-16T11:36:36.000Z","uid":48083,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"8ce823f387c3b5defde3391e7df861c4c6b29369","tid":1785430,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T11:05:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/12/16/190432_b65950700522fbfb6b407b1342f22e64.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F12%2F16%2F190432_b65950700522fbfb6b407b1342f22e64.png&h=e6299ac4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港警察facebook圖片<br />\n昨日網上流傳相片，懷疑警方故意將槍械遺留在沙田沙角邨後樓梯間，警方今日在 fb 和記者會主動澄清，現場的懷疑槍枝只是汽槍，和警方無關，批評有「別有用心」的人，以假消息煽動憎恨警方，分化警民關係，影響執法。<br />\n<br />\n網上流傳的圖片顯示，有一個類似槍袋掛在沙田沙角邨後樓梯間，內有一枝黑色手槍，警方在 fb 發文，指網上有謠言指，警方故意遺留槍械製造恐慌，事實是警方接到保安報案，發現懷疑槍械，警方到場後證實手槍只是氣槍，批評有人用假消息煽動市民，分化警民關係。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E7%B6%B2%E5%82%B3%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E6%B2%99%E8%A7%92%E9%82%A8%E5%BE%8C%E6%A8%93%E6%A2%AF%E9%81%BA%E4%B8%8B%E6%89%8B%E6%A7%8D-%E8%AD%A6-%E5%8F%AA%E6%98%AF%E6%B1%BD%E6%A7%8D-%E5%88%A5%E6%9C%89%E7%94%A8%E5%BF%83%E5%81%87%E6%B6%88%E6%81%AF%E7%85%BD%E5%8B%95%E6%86%8E%E6%81%A8%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E5%2582%25B3%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2596%25B9%25E6%25B2%2599%25E8%25A7%2592%25E9%2582%25A8%25E5%25BE%258C%25E6%25A8%2593%25E6%25A2%25AF%25E9%2581%25BA%25E4%25B8%258B%25E6%2589%258B%25E6%25A7%258D-%25E8%25AD%25A6-%25E5%258F%25AA%25E6%2598%25AF%25E6%25B1%25BD%25E6%25A7%258D-%25E5%2588%25A5%25E6%259C%2589%25E7%2594%25A8%25E5%25BF%2583%25E5%2581%2587%25E6%25B6%2588%25E6%2581%25AF%25E7%2585%25BD%25E5%258B%2595%25E6%2586%258E%25E6%2581%25A8%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2596%25B9%2F&d=dVEf9brN%2BTtwApumOSMW7nXW3JPDzH8o%2FFP8rJ6jlcg%3D&h=6ff3f2d2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3